Name: DeepSea
About the game: Move the shield with simple controls and keep the jellyfish safe! Be careful of various obstacles under the sea. Venture through the endless sea and aim for the highest score! Features - Beautiful undersea graphics - Simple one-finger drag control - Endless gameplay - Unique obstacles and various stage levels - Unlock various skins
